snippet.title: Killerwatt C64 Longplay [171] Full Playthrough / Walkthrough (no commentary) #c64 #retrogaming
snippet.description:
Longplay of the 1984 C64 classic Killerwatt , recorded by Eric, published 15 February 2019.

Killerwatt release dates:
- C64: 1984

Killerwatt is longplay No. 332 of the Ludophiles longplays project:
- https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLFXG3BI19O5rpA9sB1_-K_x5s207hoahb
- http://www.ludophiles.com/threads/ludophiles-longplays-project.180/

Killerwatt is longplay No. 171 of RecordedC64Games.org:
- https://recordedc64games.org/killerwatt/

More C64 longplays on our playlist:
- https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLFXG3BI19O5pV-0T6Gyj6Vg66zMR3q-kH

Some highlights from that playlist:
- Raid Over Moscow https://youtu.be/SaTe_7uoGDw (caused some political tension)
- Project Firestart https://youtu.be/sUb-oWAkuX0 (founded a genre)
- The Last Ninja https://youtu.be/TPPlJhpE_9Y (the soundtrack alone is a piece of art)
- Ghosts 'n Goblins Arcade https://youtu.be/FcLFi0aPKzw (fantastic remake & expansion)
- Labyrinth https://youtu.be/brwWzMKD4rg (the first ever "LucasArts" adventure)

Subscribe to the Ludophiles channel:
- https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfbYu2svVCnAdMLaZOhAasw?sub_confirmation=1

Become a Ludophiles channel member:
- https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfbYu2svVCnAdMLaZOhAasw/join

#ludophiles #ludophilia #c64 #retrogaming #longplay #playthrough
